Reference:  https://www.freebsd.org/doc/handbook/updating-upgrading-freebsdupdate.html

To upgrade to a new point release or major version:

# freebsd-update fetch
# freebsd-update install  (updates packages for current release)
# shutdown -r now
# freebsd-update -r XX.Y-RELEASE upgrade
# freebsd-update install  (installs new kernel)
# shutdown -r now
# freebsd-update install  (updates additional packages)
# shutdown -r now
